text: Vasil Konstantinov (born 15 March 1929) is a Bulgarian gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1952 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1929 births Category:Living people Category:Bulgarian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Bulgaria Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
